  "texts": [
    "Kinect has a low scanning resolution but a fast image registration rate (30 frames per second) [155].",
    "It contains two cameras and an infrared emitter.",
    "Six participants between the ages of 26 and 50 took part in the study.",
    "Each experiment participant sat at a distance of 2 ms from the Kinect device in a sitting position.",
    "A participant's task was to play mimic effects according to instructions on a computer screen."
  ],
